=== PLASMA_JELLYFISH ===
# id: 31
# title: The Plasma Jellyfish
# chinese_title: 等离子水母
# category: Alien
# mode: dungeon

Translucent creatures drift through a flooded section of the station, their bodies crackling with contained plasma. They pulse with gentle light, seemingly docile. One bumps against your leg, sending a tingle of static through your suit's shielding.

* [Follow the jellyfish — they seem to be going somewhere]
  ~ gain_radical("水")
  "水" (shuǐ) — water, liquid, fluid
* [Collect plasma residue from their trail]
  ~ gain_item("emp_grenade")
  "电" (diàn) — electricity
* [Wade through carefully to the exit]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "游" (yóu) — to swim, to travel
